Checksums-Sha256:
 943d3bf22ac661fb0f59bc4ff68cc12b04ff17a838dfcc2537008eb9c7f3770a 3 pkg-no-md5_1.0.dsc
 90aebae315675cbf04612de4f7d5874850f48e0b8dd82becbeaa47ca93f5ebfb 3 pkg-no-md5_1.0.tar.gz

Package: pkg-mixed-ok
