Version: 1.0
Maintainer: Joe Sixpack <joe@example.org>
Architecture: all
Checksums-Sha1:
 680254bad1d7ca0d65ec46aaa315d363abf6a50a 3 pkg-mixed-ok_1.0.tar.gz
